  "texts": [
    "The total number of scaffolded elements refers to all the key elements with which students initially struggled but achieved after using the support during practice.",
    "The value of the scaffolding apply rate is from 0 to 1, where zero means the student was unable to apply any elements they got from the practice support when answering the posttest.",
    "This suggests the student did not retain anything from using the support during practice.",
    "One means that the student was able to apply all the elements obtained from the practice support in the posttest.Out of the 18 participants, 14 (77.8%) used the programming support for all four practice problems.",
    "Therefore, to balance the data, we only included these 14 participants to answer RQ1 and RQ2."
  ],
